><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">安永</span></strong></p></li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">专门成立了<strong style="outline: 0px;">ESG咨询公司安永碳业（EY carbon）</strong>，并计划投资一亿英镑。</span><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">未来3年内招聘1300人，并推出了行业内首个采用机器人技术的ESG管理平台。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.6em;"><br style="outline: 0px;"></p><ul class="list-paddingleft-1" style="width: 577.068px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);list-style-type: circle;"><li style="outline: 0px;"><p style="outline: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><strong style="outline: 0px;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">德勤</span></strong></p></li></ul><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &