d rgb(239, 248, 248);visibility: visible;"><p data-mid="" mpa-is-content="t" style="margin-bottom: -6px;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;line-height: 21px;letter-spacing: 2px;visibility: visible;"><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(40, 167, 169);letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;">05&nbsp;</span><span style="outline: 0px;color: rgb(40, 167, 169);visibility: visible;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;">CFA的ESG证书优势</span></p></div></div><p data-mid="" mpa-from-tpl="t" style="margin-top: -3px;margin-right: 6px;outline: 0px;width: 8px;height: 7px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;align-self: flex-end;z-index: 1;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.875" data-w="16" style="outline: 0px;display: initial;visibility: visible !important;width: 16px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/aU7yG8jibIeqADHk9RNpPjf4cIdO08KhSCcUQRA04fq16196c6Nvic8k3CYoMfxZodiblF4IDAQB5FdicOdy5vaovg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1"></p></div></div></div></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1" data-w="64" style="height: 20px !important;max-height: 20px !important;width: 20px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6Un8z2WcpUjD7iaAJtaMK87RCxS5k4Riawibz18PI6mOsP7lbqWmQknnktQ/640?wx_fmt=png">&nbsp;<strong>教材体系完整，实用性强</strong></span><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;">备考过CFA的同学都知道，<strong>CFA协会的教材向来以体系完整著称，ESG证书也是找专业的人编写的教材</strong>。读完这本书，就是最系统的学习ESG知识了<strong>，</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">读最少的书、学最系统的知识。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1" data-w="64" style="height: 20px !important;max-height: 20px !important;width: 20px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6Un8z2WcpUjD7iaAJtaMK87RCxS5k4Riawibz18PI6mOsP7lbqWmQknnktQ/640?wx_fmt=png"><strong>&nbsp;文科生友好</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong>考试内容也不涉及任何计算题，全部都是定性的问题，</strong>考试的时候甚至不让你拿计算机。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1" data-w="64" style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;height: 20px !important;max-height: 20px !important;width: 20px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6Un8z2WcpUjD7iaAJtaMK87RCxS5k4Riawibz18PI6mOsP7lbqWmQknnktQ/640?wx_fmt=png"><strong style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;">&nbsp;大学生可考</strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;">本科期间可以考试、含金量又高的证书其实并不多。<strong>而ESG大学期间完全可以考，既可以快速拿证，又有CFA的头衔。找相关实习更是一个很好的背书。</strong></span><strong style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;"><br></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><strong style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;"><br></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1" data-w="64" style="height: 20px !important;max-height: 20px !important;width: 20px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6Un8z2WcpUjD7iaAJtaMK87RCxS5k4Riawibz18PI6mOsP7lbqWmQknnktQ/640?wx_fmt=png"><strong>&nbsp;考试灵活，快速拿证</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;">不论是<strong>国内还是海外，都可以随时在家预约网络考位</strong>。考完当场出成绩，快速拿证。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1" data-w="64" style="height: 20px !important;max-height: 20px !important;width: 20px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6Un8z2WcpUjD7iaAJtaMK87RCxS5k4Riawibz18PI6mOsP7lbqWmQknnktQ/640?wx_fmt=png"><strong>早</strong><strong>期福利，通过率高</strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;">由于ESG证书还处在红利期，考试通过率高达70%。不过随着ESG热度增加，后期考试难度也有可能会水涨船高。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><strong><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">所以</span><span style="font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;">考试要趁早，千万别等它变难了、考试的人多了、竞争激烈了再考。</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;"><br></span></span></p><div data-mid="" mpa-from-tpl="t" style="margin-bottom: 0px;padding-top: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;width: 553.785px;background: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UEl7Gm0kiaEMicrBvnmWTx0XEOvjzIhOO4L4FXc03P7Eys15iaJ231pUhU6pNxeEpekicyXqWbgsvZfzJcgvQZ52Gg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;) 0% 0% / 400px repeat 