S 方案，yyds！" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="11" tab="innerlink" style="letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 12px;text-align: left;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;" data-linktype="2">4 种 MySQL 同步 ES 方案，yyds！</a></p></div></div></div><div data-support="96编辑器" data-style-id="19744" style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><div><p><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NjMwMDg0Ng==&amp;mid=2455380492&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=8a9a7a6d8efdacd08731fc678a4aadde&amp;chksm=871cb84db06b315b82e708be4aa7914012fb079fd279a63278da89ddeb8c300fe9d8a8d6f5af&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="一个指令，释放 1000 行屎山代码" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" style="font-size: 14px;" data-linktype="2"><span style="font-size: 14px;">一个指令，释放 1000 行屎山代码</span></a><br></p><p><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NjMwMDg0Ng==&amp;mid=2455380484&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=b76b3dd334ecf29caf57be34d797ab7b&amp;chksm=871cb845b06b3153b1bcc8fc7de5cfb654fc9cb0d90ae714d8318731fdd60f1bbbd4cb14179a&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="苹果在macOS中“魔改”cURL，作者无端背锅很生气：误导用户！" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" style="font-size: 14px;" data-linktype="2"><span style="font-size: 14px;">苹果在macOS中“魔改”cURL，作者无端背锅很生气：误导用户！</span></a><br></p><p><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5NjMwMDg0Ng==&amp;mid=2455380479&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=50345fc05bec5a0a2433aa1c20572bdf&amp;chksm=871cbbbeb06b32a8e2ebaaa1bc8205d9ae6a83aa1c4c8fc816b9b7d9447fc3c0a6557422d1aa&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="大厂的骄傲？把钱存下来更实际！" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2" style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">大厂的骄傲？把钱存下来更实际！</span></a><br></p>